data.description: Nestled in the Masterplanned community of Lakemont, this stunning home offers 4 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms. Upon entering, you'll be immediately struck by soaring ceilings allowing an abundance of natural light. The sizable kitchen provides ample counter space, high-end appliances, and a well-thought-out layout. The first floor primary suite is spacious with vaulted ceilings, a walk-in closet, double sinks with a vanity area, jetted tub and separate shower. Upstairs you will find 3 generously sized bedrooms, a great game room & separate media/office. Lastly, the backyard offers a fully fenced yard with a large covered patio and no back neighbors perfect for privacy.
